Class QiimeOpenRefClassifier

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BioModule, ClassifierModule, ScriptModule

    public class QiimeOpenRefClassifier
extends QiimeClassifier
implements ClassifierModule
    This module runs the QIIME pick_open_reference_otus.py script on FastA sequence files in a single script so it is important to allocate sufficient job resources if running in a clustered environment.

    • Method Detail

      • buildScript

        public List<List<String>> buildScript(List<File> files)
                               throws Exception
        Return bash script lines to pick open reference OTUs by passing the newest biom file in the temp directory [via bash code "$(ls -t $tempDir/*.biom | head -1)"] to QiimeClassifier getPickOtuLines() method.

        Several biom files are generated by this script, the script will select biomFile =
        If property "qiime.removeChimeras" = "Y", use vsearch to identify chimeras and call "filter_otus_from_otu_table.py" to remove them from "otu_table.biom"

        Specified by:
        buildScript in interface ScriptModule
        Overrides:
        buildScript in class QiimeClassifier
        Parameters:
        files - Files in the input directory that contain only forward reads
        Returns:
        Nested list of bash scripts lines
        Throws:
        Exception - if unable to generate script lines

      • checkDependencies

        public void checkDependencies()
                       throws Exception
        Call QiimeClassifier checkOtuPickingDependencies() method to verify OTU picking script parameters. If not in Docker mode and property "qiime.removeChimeras" = "Y", verify "exe.vsearch" and "exe.vsearchParams".
        Specified by:
        checkDependencies in interface BioModule
        Overrides:
        checkDependencies in class QiimeClassifier
        Throws:
        Exception - thrown if missing or invalid dependencies are found

      • executeTask

        public void executeTask()
                 throws Exception
        Call buildScript(List) to create bash script lines for open reference OTU picking. Pass lines to BashScriptBuilder.buildScripts(biolockj.module.ScriptModule, List, int) to create the bash script. Pass 1 as last parameter since all reads are processed in a single batch.
        Specified by:
        executeTask in interface BioModule
        Overrides:
        executeTask in class ScriptModuleImpl
        Throws:
        Exception - thrown if the module is unable to complete is task
